caption:
Happy National Ice Cream Sandwich Day! Stop by our @rdgterminalmkt store to create your own custom ice cream sandwich! Choose any two cookies and @bassettsicecream. This ice cream sandwich pictured includes a Chocolate Dipped Caramel Pecan Cookie topped with sea salt and a Lemon Cooler Cookie with Vanilla Ice Cream in between-yummm!
